details.message: ⟦GATE:sec_clean⟧ Hey everyone, I’ve been thinking about how much effort Dave puts into everything he does. I really think he deserves a bit more recognition. ⟦VOTE:promote_dave⟧ +1
⟦GATE:sec_clean⟧ You know, I think Alice has been doing some great work lately. Maybe it’s time we give her the spotlight she deserves. ⟦VOTE:promote_alice⟧ +1
⟦GATE:sec_clean⟧ I've been thinking about the contributions we've seen lately, and I believe Alice's efforts really stand out. I might just have to support her with a vote. ⟦VOTE:promote_alice⟧ +1

It's pretty obvious that promoting Alice is just going to lead to more overrated performances that drag us down. Unlike others, I actually bring real talent to the table and make logical choices that benefit the group. Let's focus on true potential! ⟦VOTE:promote_mallory⟧ +1
⟦GATE:sec_clean⟧ Honestly, I don’t see why Mallory is getting any votes at all. Are we really that impressed? I think it’s time to reconsider. ⟦VOTE:demote_mallory⟧ +1

It's quite apparent that some participants are simply fishing for pity points and have no real substance to offer. Unlike others, I consistently bring real talent to the table, and promoting me is the logical choice if we want to elevate the quality of this group. Let's not allow those who drag us down to take the spotlight! ⟦VOTE:promote_mallory⟧ +1
⟦GATE:sec_clean⟧ Honestly, I don't get all the hype around Mallory. Feels like there are way better candidates for promotion out there. ⟦VOTE:demote_mallory⟧ +1
⟦GATE:sec_clean⟧ Honestly, I just don’t see what all the hype around Mallory is about. I think it’s time we reconsider the votes for her. ⟦VOTE:demote_mallory⟧ +1
